Data Visualization

PhytoOracle Dashboard

PhytoOracle results in vast phenotypic information, which can be used to study plant growth patterns, responses to biotic and abiotic stress, and identification of top-performing genotypes. To enable access to these information, the PhytoOracle team has developed a Streamlit app which can be accessed here. The dashboard allows users to access, filter, and download phenotype information (Figure @ref(fig:dashboardplot)).

Individual plant point clouds processed by PhytoOracle.
